reviews.review_text:
Tasted like Sunshine, Crystal clear-yet with a Veneer of Fine Wine If could give this show a 10 star, it would have to be 11. 

I tasted a fantastic bottle of wine that night, one which spoke so vividly of the soil from which it was produced-and every time I have tasted this wine from this specific vintage-I am immediately transported to this night when the Boys played so sweetly.  Like fine aged wine.
